title: Transylbabies
description: A mission to babysit Snowmanpire babies in Transylbiria leads Vambre and Prohyas to attack the local monster townsfolk in misguided attempts to keep the Snowbabies safe.

title: Caillou at the Water Park
description: Caillou goes to the water park and faces pirates, races down lazy river, and rides a big slide!

title: Skips' Stress
description: Skips has to lower his stress before it kills him.

title: Caillou's Class Pet
description: It's Caillou's turn to take Gerald the class pet home, but when Caillou isn't careful, Gerald disappears!

title: #RageCat
description: Jessica Cruz is convinced she can find the purr-fect forever home for Dexter, a cat who has been deemed unadoptable because he's basically the worst cat in the world. Her overbearing persistence in trying to get him adopted leads Dexter to become Dex-Starr, an evil Red Lantern supervillain! Can Jess still find the good in a fuzzy little nemesis who is trying to kill her?

title: Los Maestros Nunca se Rinden
description: Cole, la princesa Vania, Wu y los humildes llegan a un templo, que una vez fue un campo de entrenamiento para los Maestros Elementales de la Tierra.

title: Planet X
description: When Rad returns to his home planet, he learns a shocking truth about alien society.

title: Guardian of the Unikingdom
description: Hawkodile insists the Unikingdom is more dangerous than it looks and sets out to prove it by taking his friends on bodyguard patrol.

title: Caillou at the Theme Park
description: Caillou goes to the theme park and rides his first rollercoaster!

title: Drawn to Sports with Hannah
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Hannah competes in track and field.

title: La Hora Mas Oscura
description: Los Ninjas, los Munces y los Geckles se refugian en la Cueva Fuerte Geckle , pero enfrentan al Hechicero Calavera y al Dragón Grief-Bringer.

title: Freeze!
description: Axel and his team find themselves in a tough position after Ice Crusher makes it too cold for them to fight back at full speed.

title: #AmigasDelAlma Parte 1
description: En este episodio especial de dos partes, las chicas deben rastrear a Katana, una guerrera misteriosa que está robando las almas de los villanos de Metrópolis. Mientras tanto, Tatsu, la nueva amiga de Diana, es su alma gemela en todo sentido, ipero puede que tenga una conexión con Katana!
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Past Aliens Present
description: After Ben stumbles upon a video of Cannonbolt ripping up a computer lab on the internet, Team Tennyson must race to State U to find the imposter; but once Ben discovers it is a steam-punk version of his alien that is terrorizing the campus, Ben must take down the man behind the machine, Steam Smythe!

title: O Mother, Where Art Thou?
description: Ma Vreedle threatens to blow up the sun if Ben and the Plumbers don't find her missing son!

title: Cellie
description: Fed up with sharing, Panda forbids his brothers from using his cellphone any longer. But when the brothers get their own super advanced smartphones, Panda starts to succumb to crippling jealousy.

title: Fashion Bears
description: In order to abide by the clothing policy of their favorite Boba shop, the Bears get some new outfits. But with new looks come new lives including office work, fashion modeling and even falling in love!

title: Reststop Roustabout
description: With the Rustbucket stopped on the Midwest roadside, Ben locks himself inside with his tablet as Max and Gwen enjoy the great outdoors, until Team Tennyson is pulled into a wild Jack-a-Lope chase.

title: Sneakerheads
description: Apple & Onion need a Last Will and Testament if they are to protect their belongings from the state.

title: Atchoo
description: Meet Bing and his friends… Join us and celebrate the noisy, joyful, messy reality of preschool life.

title: Caillou's Garden Fort
description: Caillou and Daddy build a fort in the garden.

title: Sunday Brunch/Caillou to the Rescue/Caillou's Top Bunk/Recipe For Fun
description: Caillou, Dad and Rosie take Mom out for Sunday brunch to celebrate Mother's Day./Gilbert gets caught up a tree, and to Caillou's delight a fire truck full of firefighters has to be called in to rescue him./Caillou and Rosie get to spend the night at Grandma and Grandpa's house./Dad drives Caillou to Grandma's for the day.

title: Caillou Goes Back to School
description: Caillou gets ready for his first day back at school and Mommy packs him a lunchbox surprise!

title: The Beepers: The Visitor
description: The Beepers find the perfect groove after a new friend shreds a little too hard.

title: Fathers and Friends/Midsummer Nightmare
description: Midsummer Nightmare: Drago and the other AO Bakugan face an unseen threat with earth shattering power only to be left wondering if it was all a dream./Father's and Fiends: Osamu Kazami comes to take his son Shun back home and finds a defiance he hadn't counted on.

title: Sunken Treasure
description: A relaxing beach day becomes an underwater adventure when Unikitty and her friends find a message in a bottle.

title: Caillou Has a Spooky Sleepover
description: Caillou and his friends tell spooky stories at a sleepover!

title: Two Parter Part 1
description: The Titans visit the Hall of Justice to use the pool, but then decide to check out the inside.

title: Land of the Lost Shadows
description: When pieces of their shadows are stolen by a shadow demon, Uncle Grandpa and the gang must travel to the Land of Lost Shadows in order to retrieve them.

title: Masters Never Quit
description: Pursued by a magma monster, Cole, Princess Vania, Wu & the Lowly arrive at a mysterious temple deep in Shintaro Mountain, a temple which was once a training ground for Earth Elementals including Cole's own mother, Lilly!

title: Porque tan triste?
description: Steven ha escuchado rumores de un par de Gemas que todavía están destruyendo mundos. Si él no puede detenerlas, tal vez Lapis sí.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Dumbrella
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, have been traveling on the back of a truck in the rain for days. Charlie produces an umbrella to help his friend but unfortunately it's a "dumbrella" and it's looking to have some fun with them!

title: The Tig-Tale Heart
description: When the office becomes obsessed with a Baby Bobo toy that Tiggy and Gweeseek found, a jealous Tiggy decides to put an end to its song and dance moves for good.

title: Don't Read the Comments
description: An obsession with comments and criticisms about him on the Board of Opinions drives Prohyas nuts, affecting Warrior missions for the worse and raising Vambre's ire, I mean, concerns.

title: Caillou Goes Ice Skating
description: Caillou and his family go ice skating!

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: Caillou and the Holiday Tree
description: Caillou and his family go to a tree farm to find a holiday tree.

title: Sleepy Bird's Surprise
description: Sleepy Bird's egg takes on a life of its own. Pocoyo and Pato have to get it back to the nest - just in time for it to hatch.

title: The Compilation
description: A compilation of some of the funniest, most bizarre clips uploaded onto the internet by the people of Elmore. Clips include Banana Joe's self-choreographed acrobatics, Richard's latest culinary invention and Gumball and Darwin's contest for who can pull the weirdest face.

title: Gryffindor v Hufflepuff
description: Dame Helen Mirren hosts the first episode of this epic TV event series. Over 4 episodes the Houses of Hogwarts will do battle to see which team knows the most about the wizarding world, featuring celebrity guests, actors from the original films and more Harry Potter Magic than you could find on a day trip to Diagon Alley. Tonight's match up sees the brave Gryffindors face the loyal Hufflepuffs for a guaranteed place in the grand finale.
originalseriesname: Harry Potter: Hogwarts Tournament of Houses

title: Head Chef
description: Mao Mao faces off with Badgerclops in a competition to determine whether cooking (and being a hero) is an art or a science.

title: Snow Day
description: The babies experience their first snowfall.

title: Caillou Beats the Heat/Back Seat Driver/Lost and Found/Holiday Magic
description: It's hot and steamy and Mom won't let Caillou go to the public pool./Caillou, Dad and Rosie are in the car on their way to meet Mom./When Dad and Caillou find a scruffy dog that appears to be lost they bring it home./Caillou and his family pay a visit to Santa and go Christmas tree shopping all in the same day.

title: Let It Bee
description: Wanting to rush off to climb Mush Mountain, Mush-Mush is in a hurry checking nectar level in flowers - a job that takes time and care. Soon Mush-Mush's haste causes disaster when he scares all the bees away. Now Mush-Mush and friends have to find a way to lure the bees back…

title: Dream Boat
description: Sumo devotes himself to the Sisyphean task of building a boat, defying the expectations of everyone in his life, including himself.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Wednesday - Part 4
description: Elliott and his mom Frankie are about to have a Wednesday they'll never forget, when a mysterious rock unexpectedly transports them somewhere across the universe. Finding themselves in a strange new environment with strange new creatures, they meet a dinosaur named Mo - and that's just the beginning of their out of this world adventure!

title: The Eater
description: It's Halloween and Apple's not feeling quite right. He takes Onion into the dark depths to find out why.

title: Caillou and the Bird
description: Caillou tries to nurse a baby bird back to health.

title: Out of My Head
description: Axel must help Sarge and Bobbie learn to walk in each other's shoes - literally - after Luka unwittingly switches the toys' heads!

title: Drummer Boy
description: Pocoyo wants to drum, but his friends are all busy playing different things. Pocoyo learns that sometimes his friends don't want to do exactly the same things as him.

title: Stratified/Maze Daze
description: Stratified: The AO embark on a mission into the mysterious labyrinth world of Vestroia to find Strata the Hunter and free the Bakugan he has imprisoned./Maze Daze: Lost in the maze of Vestroia the AO encounter powerful forces that seem to be struggling for control over the alien landscape.

title: Matter of the Mind/Core Cell
description: Matter of Mind: Drago leads the Bakugan against the threat of Tiko to protect a powerful energy source called the Core Cell./Core Cell: The AO defend the Core Cell from an attack by Tiko and in a last ditch effort to save it Dan manages to evolve Drago into his L2 form.

title: Meet Cheetara
description: Cheetara is the coolest cat around! Not only is she so fast that she can outrun lightning, but so clever she can outsmart Mumm-Ra's evil plans! Villains don't stand a chance against Cheetara…well, unless Mumm-Ra uses his Doom Staff, then she might be in trouble.

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

title: Caillou and the Rash
description: Caillou wakes up an itchy rash.

title: Backwards Day
description: It's Backwards Day! But Thomas misunderstands the game and accidentally delivers the wrong cargo to the wrong places.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Ahora Te Toca a Ti, Amigo
description: Axel y el equipo giran las bromas de camuflaje de Galileo sobre él, convenciendo al crédulo gecko de que es permanentemente invisible, ipara obtener resultados desastrosos!

title: Caillou the Cupid
description: Caillou is chosen to be Class Cupid and gets to deliver Valentine's Cards to all his friends!

title: Caillou and the Dolphins
description: Caillou goes swimming with Dolphins at the aquarium with his family.

title: Caillou and the Rock Pools
description: Caillou meets new sea creatures while exploring rock pools at the beach!

title: Goose Chase
description: While at the park, Clarence happily feeds some birds his sandwich, imagining himself as their king. He has a great time until one persistent goose will not leave him alone!

title: #AbracadabraPalooza
description: En un intento por hacer que Karen se sienta mejor con un granito que le salió, Zee le cuenta la avergonzante transición que le dio poderes mágicos y la grieta que eso generó entre ella y su padre.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Caillou on the Slopes
description: Caillou shares a story about his first time going skiing.

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: Meet Lion-O
description: Meet Lion-O and the Thundercats! After fleeing their home planet, the Thundercats find themselves stranded on Third Earth where they face the evil Mumm-Ra. But Lion-O is strong! He's tough! There's nothing he can't do! Except maybe open really big jars of cookies…

title: #SoulSisters Part 1
description: The girls must track down Katana, a mysterious warrior who's stealing the souls of Metropolis's villains. Meanwhile, Diana's new friend Tatsu is a perfect match for her in every way, but may have a connection to Katana.

title: Continue?
description: The Mysterious Hooded Woman hires the Warriors to retrieve the Orb of Sphericity from a temple in Galacton. The odd thing is, this temple has save points! When the Warriors are defeated, they respawn, but Vambre remembers what happened and Prohyas does not.

title: Caillou in the Castle
description: King Caillou and Queen Clementine build a castle together using boxes!

title: #GatoRabioso
description: Jessica Cruz está convencida de que puede conseguirle un hogar definitivo perfecto para Dexter, un gato que la gente considera inadoptable porque, básicamente, es el peor gato del mundo.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Dust Buddies
description: As punishment for making a huge mess in their house, Belson's mom makes Belson clean up, offering their usual maid service to Mary and Clarence. Embarrassed of their messy house, Mary and Clarence hurry to clean up before the maid arrives.

title: Spin Out
description: Taz learns a tough lesson. He shouldn't spin after eating too much candy.

title: La Celula Nucleo
description: Los Fantásticos defienden la Célula Núcleo de un ataque de Tiko, y en el último intento de Dan por salvarla, él y Drago logran liberar un nuevo poder.

title: Caillou at the Aquarium
description: Caillou visits the aquarium on a school trip and spots a seahorse, a scuba diver and a sea lion!

title: Caillou at the World Food Fair
description: Caillou visits a fair and tries different foods from around the world!

title: Dino Club
description: Pressured to choose a real job, Seth instead decides to be a dinosaur like Pam! Soon, all the kids follow suit, but cause so much trouble, Fungietown bans dinosaurs! But Pam can't stop being a dinosaur and is thrown in jail!

title: El Dragon Grief-Bringer
description: Nya y Kai, quienes se han convertido en los líderes de los Munces y Geckles, intentan unirlos para derrotar a su enemigo mutuo, el Hechicero Calavera.

title: Cast Aside the Truth
description: Hawkodile breaks his arm in a careless spill and lies to his friends about the accident to keep from looking bad.

title: Caillou's Show and Tell
description: Caillou has a show and tell, and learns that being patient can teach him cool new things!

title: Demonios Internos
description: Los Fantásticos encuentran la forma de salir de Vestroia, pero descubren que en realidad están en un mundo paralelo.

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Brain Drain
description: Missing memories provide an intriguing mystery for everyone's favorite young female heroes in this all-new animated film.  When Supergirl, Wonder Woman, Batgirl, Harley Quinn, Bumblebee, Poison Ivy and Katana suddenly realize they cannot remember a single moment from their Monday at Super Hero High, the young Super Heroes spring into sleuthing action! Suspecting foul-play, they band together to retrace their steps and uncover the mystery of who exactly stole their memories - and, what nefarious plan might be afoot?

title: Drawn to Sports with Luke
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Luke is passionate about running, jumping and climbing in Ninja Racing.

title: Caillou and Pepper
description: Caillou spends a day at the park and plays with a dog named Pepper!

title: Summer BBQ
description: Caillou tells his class about the exciting BBQ he had on the weekend!

title: Caillou at the Zoo
description: Caillou goes to the zoo and meets an elephant, a lion and a monkey!

title: #TheGoodTheBadAndTheBizarre
description: Everything is going well for Kara Danvers, both as a teen and a superhero, until she starts taking the blame for things she didn't do, and the emergence of a new supervillain threatens to destroy Supergirl's hard-earned reputation.

title: The Disaster
description: When Rob purchases a universal remote from the Awesome Store, he discovers can control the entire universe. He rewinds into the past and remembers Gumball had left him in The Void, leaving him scarred and in his current mutated shape. He uses the universal remote to destroy Gumball's life, whilst Gumball has to figure out what's going on before he's ejected once and for all.

title: #Abracadabrapalooza
description: In an attempt to make Karen feel better about a pimple, Zee recounts her embarrassing transition into magichood, and the rift it created between her and her father.

title: Cuenta Regresiva
description: Axel tiene que limpiar la sala de estar a tiempo para la cena de su tío, pero tratar de hacer demasiado de una vez lo deja atrapado como un juguete con Orangutank suelto y menos de una hora hasta que lleguen los invitados.

title: Caillou the Wizard
description: Caillou visits an old castle and pretends he is a wizard.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Bearly Edible
description: After eating the snacks meant for everyone and replacing them with disgusting low budget cookies from Barfvomita, Owen is full of guilt (and cookies) and tries to make things right.

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: Dollar Hunt
description: Clarence hosts a fun "dollar hunt" game to meet new friends. But things go awry when Clarence accidentally buries the money his Mom gave him to buy refreshments for her book club meeting.

title: El sentimiento
description: Mientras Max y Gwen se deleitan en el espíritu navideño de Winter Wonderland, Ben no podría estar más aburrido y concentrado en los juguetes. Pero cuando los Weatherheads fijan sus miras en Winter Wonderland como su próximo objetivo, nuestro héroe debe conectarse con sus emociones si quiere salvar la ciudad.

title: Home Sweet Home
description: Lucas, Findley and Bodhi discover a yummy gingerbread house and immediately devour it. Feeling like the fun is over, they head to bed. But the next morning, they are surprised to find a new gingerbread house and, assuming it was fixed by magic, they decide it's too special to eat.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Big City Dancers
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, traveling on the back of a truck visit NYC where the rhythms of the city make Charlie wanna dance his little back porch off. Frank … not so much. But when you go far enough into the city, anything can happen.

title: Teachers
description: When Darwin asks his friends which teacher deserves to be on the yearbook cover, they struggle to find a single worthy candidate! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Spy-ou
description: Secret Agents Sarah and Caillou try and steal a diamond from Rosie's secret lair.

title: Around the World
description: Caillou takes a trip around the world and visits the plains of Africa, the Arctic, ancient Egypt, and Paris.

title: Adopt a Jackal
description: After a battle with the Mutants, Jackalman gets confused and accidentally returns to the Cats' Lair with the Thundercats, he is the dumbest mutant. Jackalman pretends to be a Thundercat so his enemies won't catch him and the Thundercats pretend to play along because they feel bad for him!

title: Caillou and the Easter Egg Hunt
description: Caillou searches for chocolate eggs in the park with his friends!

title: Joke's on You, Bro!
description: Axel and the team turn Galileo's camouflaging pranks around on him, convincing the gullible gecko that he's permanently invisible - to disastrous results!

title: Superfriends
description: The new girl next door learns it's hard to be best friends with superheroes and soon starts hanging out with the wrong kind of kid, Princess.

title: All Chalked Up
description: Him tricks Bubbles into bringing her chalk drawings to life, who then proceed to wreak havoc in Townsville.

title: Brother Builder
description: As Craig races against time to build a super important invention, we learn how Craig became such a clever inventor!

title: Ranger Tabes
description: To recover a missing package, the Bears get help from Ranger Tabes, an eccentric forest ranger. But her overblown sense of justice might be too much for the Bears to handle.

title: Caillou Goes to Work
description: Caillou helps Daddy with grown-up work on Take Your Kid to Work Day!

title: Caillou on Sports Day
description: Caillou takes part in the egg race and learns to keep trying and never give up!

title: We Baby Bears: BHA Bha Song
description: We Baby Bears follows baby bear brothers Grizz, Panda, and Ice Bear as they journey in a magical box to fantastic different worlds in search of their perfect home.

title: Power Up Puff
description: During a fight, both Buttercup and Bubbles are surprised to discover they've leveled up, leaving Blossom to wonder when or if she'll get new powers too.

title: Chip's Damage
description: Elodie enlists KO to help figure out what to do about Chip Damage.

title: Man Up
description: When Buttercup's aggression inadvertently allows villain Man-Boy to escape, she starts a new-age lifestyle in an effort to be more calm. But when Man-Boy returns to enact his revenge, Buttercup must embrace the balance between punching and hugging in order to defeat him.

title: Little Graduation
description: Steven and the Gems celebrate Little Homeschool's first graduating class.

title: Downhill From Here/Next Stop Fun/Under Sail/Farmer Caillou
description: Mom, an avid skier, takes Caillou downhill skiing while Dad and Rosie sit in the cozy chalet and watch./Caillou is very excited when the family takes a trip across country by train./Caillou finds an old toy sailing boat./Mr. Hinkle invites Caillou to visit his sister's farm.

title: Keep Going Pocoyo
description: Pato and Elly are enjoying skipping with a skipping rope. Pocoyo thinks it looks like fun and he wants to skip too. Try as he might though, Pocoyo can't do it. So he asks his friends for help.

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: K.I.L.I.T. Radio
description: Muscle Man wants a local radio station to play the song he wrote for Starla.

title: Whatever Happened to... Rippy Roo?
description: Rippy Roo visits the plaza.

title: Safari Joe
description: While minding her own business, Cheetara is caught in a trap set by Safari Joe, the famously annoying hunter! After escaping, she rallies the other ThunderCats to help her stop Joe once and for all, by turning the tables and capturing him!

title: Stratificados
description: Los Fantásticos emprenden una misión en el misterioso mundo laberíntico de Vestroia para buscar a Strata El Cazador y liberar a los Bakugan que tiene presos.

title: Caillou's New Classmate
description: Caillou learns what to do when others are being mean.

title: Caillou Goes Ape
description: Caillou, Leo and Clementine go to a "high ropes" park.

title: Why So Blue?
description: Steven has heard rumors of a pair of Gems that are still destroying worlds. If he can't stop them, maybe Lapis can.

title: Caillou at the Optometrist
description: Caillou gets his first eye test and learns it's not scary at all!

title: Fun Dungeon Face Off
description: Clarence's Mom treats Clarence, Jeff and Sumo to an afternoon at Rough Riders Chicken, a fast food restaurant with a play emporium. When Clarence and Sumo steal Jeff's fries, Jeff is forced to confront his germ phobias head-on in the restaurant's seemingly unsanitary play area.

title: Caillou and the April Fools Prank
description: Caillou learns how to play fun tricks on April Fool's Day!

title: The Good, The Bad, The Caillou
description: Sheriff Caillou and Deputy Clementine thwart Leo the Bandit's train robbery.

title: Atrapados en la Jungla
description: Aún perdidos en Vestroia, Los Fantásticos experimentan los efectos de la Célula Núcleo que altera sus cuerpos, y se encuentran cara a cara con el monstruo Bakugan, Tiko.

title: Caillou's London Vacation
description: Caillou and his family visit London, and meet the Queen!

title: Field Trip
description: A group of teenage superheroes are being shown around the Fortress of Solitude when they inadvertently cause the phantom zone projector to trap Superman and release three Kryptonian criminals.

title: Charlene Mania
description: When Vic attempts to have the perfect day off, the town's sudden obsession for Charlene gets in his way.

title: Mud Is Thicker Than Water
description: Ben, Gwen and Cousin Lucy try to find out how Psyphon's thugs are getting Plumber technology.

title: Congelados
description: Axel y su equipo se encuentran en una posición difícil después de que Ice Crusher hace demasiado frío para que puedan defenderse a toda velocidad.

title: The Missing Mushlet
description: So Mushpie can take a break, Mush-Mush, Chep and Lilit offer to look after the Mushies, assuring her that everything will be fine. But a Mushie pops to become a Mushlet and escapes. Our friends find him in Muddler's clutches! Now, they must figure out a way to save the Mushlet and return the other Mushies to their cave before the return of Mushpie.

title: Wednesday - Part 3
description: Elliott and his mom Frankie are about to have a Wednesday they'll never forget, when a mysterious rock unexpectedly transports them somewhere across the universe. Finding themselves in a strange new environment with strange new creatures, they meet a dinosaur named Mo - and that's just the beginning of their out of this world adventure!

title: Star Light, Star Bright/All in a Day's Work/The Cat's Meow/Caillou in Space
description: Caillou and the family are at Grandma & Grandpa's for an evening corn roast./The house wakes up late, and that means it's a mad rush to get off to work and off to childcare./It's time for Gilbert's annual visit to the Vet./When Caillou plays astronauts with Leo he upsets Rosie.

title: Music is Everywhere
description: When music-lover Nia gets stranded before a big concert she's been waiting to see, Thomas brings the concert to her!
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: For a Few Brains More
description: Ben, Rook and Max must stop Ultimate Albedo from absorbing Azmuth's intelligence and taking over the galaxy.

title: The Beepers: Funky Time
description: The Beepers play with tempo and learn that adapting to change can be…sweaty.

title: Caillou at the Picnic
description: Caillou has a fun-filled picnic day with his friends and family.

title: Craig World
description: Craig creates an amusement park in the Creek! But when things start to get stale, he vows to make it bigger and better, no matter what it takes!

title: The Streak Part 2
description: Robin's streak of stopping 52 crimes every year is in jeopardy when members of his team are poached by Kid Flash.

title: Who's This Guy?
description: This Guy is more wound up than usual and Tiggy encourages him to take a relaxing day off. Left in charge of the office, Tig and Seek learn it's harder than they thought to keep things orderly.

title: Dungeon Crawl!
description: Having joined forces with the Lowly in their quest to defeat King Vangelis, Cole, Wu, and Vania have to find a way out of the bottom of the mountain, a place said to be inescapable.

title: The Return of Aunt Grandma
description: Aunt Grandma is back and still bent on ruining Uncle Grandpa.

title: The Cave of Gelatinous Doom!
description: The Warriors don't have a worthy adventure to use their impressive new skull-and-crossbones-emblazoned Bonehead Magisword until they are sent on a quest to battle a mighty slime beast in the Dungeon of Gelatinous Doom!

title: Caillou and the Mystery of the Missing Ball
description: Caillou and the Super Friends use their powers to save their ball from the Master Thief!

title: #AmigasDelAlma Parte 2
description: En este episodio especial de dos partes, las chicas deben rastrear a Katana, una guerrera misteriosa que está robando las almas de los villanos de Metrópolis. Mientras tanto, Tatsu, la nueva amiga de Diana, es su alma gemela en todo sentido, ipero puede que tenga una conexión con Katana!
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Pizza Eve
description: Uncle Grandpa falls for Pizza Steve's "girlfriend" and ends up in serious danger.

title: We Baby Bears Official Trailer: New Series
description: These baby bears are searching for a brand new home, and they're off to fantastical worlds and new adventures along the way. Watch the official trailer for We Baby Bears, the brand new show from the creators of We Bare Bears, coming to Cartoon Network in 2022.

title: Same Old World
description: Steven flies around the world.

title: Marcy & Hunson
description: Hunson Abadeer returns to Ooo to bond with his daughter Marceline, but will he be able to prove that he's changed his soul-sucking ways?

title: Copycat Carter
description: Craig and his friends stumble upon Carter, the cardboard genius turned cyborg, and Craig decides to help Carter become a kid again, just like him!

title: Bye Bye Bee
description: Lucas can't believe Maizie is going to leave them for the entire winter to hiber-grape so Lucas uses delaying tactics to keep her in the house.

title: Alpha Bodies
description: Cartoonito presents Alpha Bodies! It's time to use our bodies to make every letter of the alphabet, from A to Z, but one over-eager letter keeps getting ahead of itself.

title: Dawn Before Dusk
description: Dawn Before Dusk, Part 1: The AO meet Benton Dusk discovering that their quiet little corner of the world is about to become much, much larger./Dawn Before Dusk, Part 2: Benton Dusk reveals that the AO have been indentified as persons of interest by powerful corporations including Philomena Dusk's AAAnimus.

title: The Key to it All
description: Pocoyo finds a key which leads him on an exciting and magical adventure of exploration and discovery.

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Rosie's First Dentist Trip
description: Rosie is scared to go to the dentist for the first time.

title: The Ascent
description: Cole, the Lowly, Princess Vania and Wu discover that the stone-mech is fueled by Elemental Power, and attach it to the mine-carts in an effort to blast their way out of the mountain to confront the evil Skull Sorcerer!

title: Jake the Starchild
description: In order to fulfill his grand destiny, Jake is spirited away by a strangely familiar shape-shifting alien.

title: Little Octi Lost
description: Buttercup steals Octi to teach Bubbles a lesson but ends up wanting to keep him for herself.

title: Goodbye Gerald
description: Gerald the class pet passes away.

title: Caillou and the Fire Drill
description: A fire drill at school frightens Alan, a classmate with autism. Caillou tries to help Alan be less scared.

title: On the Trail of the Cloud Bouncer
description: When spores from a strange plant take over control of the Cloudseeker, Cheer and the team must risk losing the vehicle - their home away from home and their only way back to Care-A-Lot - in order to save the Whiffles' newly-planted valley.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Super Hero High
description: Supergirl arrives at Super Hero High and struggles to learn to control her new powers. Meanwhile, the Junior Detective Club investigates a mysterious rash of security breaches centered around the teleportation Boom Tubes.

title: Temple of Mars
description: Searching for answers on Mars, Finn and Jermaine discover that they must first survive a cunning Martian mental trap.

title: Sheriff Caillou
description: Sheriff Caillou rides into action to stop an outlaw from robbing the bank!

title: Caillou at the Vehicle Show
description: Caillou attends a vehicle show with grandpa and learns all about cars and trucks.

title: Bye Bye, Bellum
description: The Mayor becomes dependent on the Powerpuff Girls after his assistant Ms. Bellum departs, leaving the girls so busy they accidentally hire the dangerous Bianca Bikini as his new assistant! When Bianca captures the Powerpuff Girls, the Mayor finds the tables turned and must rely on himself to help them.

title: Caillou and the Twins
description: Caillou teams up with Jeffery and Jason to play some twin based pranks.

title: Body Swap
description: Fed up with their home experiences, Craig, Kelsey and JP agree to switch bodies!

title: Caillou and the Lost Treasure
description: Captain Caillou goes on an underwater adventure to help a mermaid find treasure!

title: Caillou the Chef
description: Caillou learns how to make fresh pasta and pizza at home!

title: Keen on Keane/Not So Awesome Blossom
description: Keen on Keane: It's Valentine's Day and the girls notice that Ms. Keane is all alone. Time for a little matchmaking, but who will be the lucky fella?/Not So Awesome Blossom: When Blossom's attack plans fail one after the other, she loses confidence in herself as the group's leader.

title: The Misunderstandings
description: Gumball has misunderstood about his date with Penny. He thought they were meeting for dinner but they were actually meeting for lunch at a Diner called Dinner. He runs to the mall but everyone he meets on the way seems to misunderstand him in a different way. Once he finally does get to the mall, it seems all his misunderstandings have caught up with him.

title: Caillou and the Anniversary Dinner
description: Caillou helps prepare for Mommy and Daddy's special wedding anniversary night.

title: Caillou Takes Pictures
description: Caillou finds an old camera and practices his colors through photography.

title: Caillou Hears a Growl
description: Caillou is worried there's a monster under his bed, so Daddy checks to make him feel better!

title: Beach Day
description: Caillou and Leo visit the beach and build sand castles, play frisbee, and paddleboard!

title: Caillou the Soccer Player
description: Caillou joins the soccer team and learns how to be a supportive teammate.

title: Padres y Amigos
description: Osamu Kazami viene para llevarse a su hijo Shun a casa y se encuentra con un obstáculo que no había contemplado.

title: Benwolf
description: In New Mexico, Max stops to visit an old friend, who's a Navajo Chief. Suddenly, a powerful storm comes out of nowhere. And behind bolts of purple lightning, a Navajo werewolf appears. As Ben battles the werewolf, he appears to be bitten and turns into Benwolf.

title: Caillou Learns to Bike
description: Caillou learns to ride his bike without training wheels like a big boy!

title: What About Cool James?
description: Seth wants some attention, but his family's too busy. But when a lucky explosion forces Cool James to stay with him, Seth gets the attention he craves! That is until Seth sees how much his family loves Cool James.

title: King Axel
description: After a screening of the King Arthur tale, Axel holds out his sword and declares himself king, but when Dynamo uses his magnetism to steal the weapon and bestow it upon Masko, it casts doubt among the team over who is the true leader.

title: Caillou and the Tooth Fairy
description: Caillou gets his first loose tooth and prepares for a visit from the Tooth Fairy!

title: The Streak Part 1
description: It's Crime Season and Robin is determined to continue his streak of stopping 52 crimes every year.

title: The Ultimate Heist
description: Albedo seeks a device that will finally change him back into his Galvan form; meanwhile, Ben is locked in Plumber HQ prison.

title: The K.O. Trap
description: KO, Rad, and Enid are caught in an especially devious trap.

title: Caillou Does Chores
description: Caillou wants a new video game and does chores to earn and allowance.

title: Steven Floats
description: Steven is so excited to be back home that he jumps for joy and jumps way too high.

title: Caillou Goes Camping
description: Caillou goes camping by a lake and discovers fun camping activities!

title: Rey Axel
description: Después de una proyección de la historia del Rey Arturo, Axel extiende su espada y se declara rey, pero cuando Dynamo usa su magnetismo para robar el arma y dársela a Masko, arroja dudas entre el equipo sobre quién es el verdadero líder.

title: Aventura en el Laberinto
description: Perdidos en el laberinto de Vestroia, Los Fantásticos se enfrentan a poderosas fuerzas que parecen luchar por el control del planeta.

title: Hello Around the World
description: Cartoonito presents Hello Around the World! All across the globe, friends greet each other in lots of different languages. Watch along and discover some of the many ways to say "Hello," around the world and beyond!

title: Holiday Show
description: Caillou's class prepares for their annual show about the holidays.

title: Caillou Rides an Airplane
description: Caillou takes his first plane trip and learns how to enjoy it safely!

title: All Jungled Up/Outer Demons
description: All Jungled Up: Still lost in Vestroia the AO experience mind altering effects of the nearby Core Cell and come face to face with the Bakuzon monster Tiko./Outer Demons: The AO find the doorway out of Vestroia only to learn they have entered a mirror world of their own imagining created by the Core Cell.

title: #SoulSisters Part 2
description: The girls must track down Katana, a mysterious warrior who's stealing the souls of Metropolis's villains. Meanwhile, Diana's new friend Tatsu is a perfect match for her in every way, but may have a connection to Katana.

title: Messy Bessy
description: Seth must clean his room and learn to be a neater person in order to keep Messy Bessy from making his life a nightmare.

title: Caillou Breaks a Bone
description: Caillou falls off his bike and breaks his arm.

title: Caillou Goes Holiday Shopping
description: Caillou goes to the mall to choose presents for his friends and Santa lends a hand!

title: Control Freak
description: When the Titans run amok in the Tower's evidence room, Robin does everything he can to keep things under control.

title: The Beepers: Spotlight
description: When a spotlight gives everyone a chance to solo, a shy Beeper discovers the courage to shine.

title: Deep Creek Salvage
description: The Trio finds gold in the muddy depths of the Creek so Craig builds a rig to recover it.

title: Gumbaldia
description: Finn and Jake, as ambassadors of the Candy Kingdom, travel to a powerful new city-state in a last ditch effort to stave off war.

title: Squideo Games
description: When Vambre and Prohyas are hired for separate gigs, they end up having to battle each other to claim a rare Squideo from Lake Sprite in Galacton.

title: La super moto
description: Duncan hace que Beth crea que rompió su bicicleta impulsada a batería y hace que lo lleve de un lugar a otro en su carrito todo el día como castigo.

title: The Blame
description: Gumball gives Billy his first taste of videogames but the sheer excitement causes him to pass out. His mother Felicity summons the PTA and threatens to ban video games all across Elmore. Gumball and Darwin are given three chances to prove that videogames can be a force for good. But when they fail, they decide to prove books can be just as dangerous.

title: Barn Mates
description: Steven helps two friends get along at the barn.

title: Summer Fun Day!
description: The Thundercats are exhausted from fighting bad guys all the time so Lion-O suggests they spend a relaxing summer fun day at the beach, with no fighting! Unfortunately the beach is home to the Crabmen, giant, clawed humanoids that fight anyone who steps on their sand! Looks like summer fun day might involve some fighting!

title: Industrias Dusk Parte 1
description: Los Fantásticos conocen a Benton Dusk y descubren que su pequeño mundo está a punto de volverse mucho más grande.

title: The Detective
description: Anais arrives in the bedroom to find a messy crime-scene and her Daisy doll missing. She realizes Gumball and Darwin are the chief suspects. Following a series of clues is her only chance to track them down and her only hope of learning what happened to Daisy. But as the mystery unravels, it seems the culprits may have turned on each other.

title: Caillou at Rosie's Birthday Party
description: Caillou has fun at Rosie's birthday party playing games and giving her a special birthday present!

title: Meet Mumm-ra and the Mutants
description: The Thundercats have met their match with the evil, undead Mumm-ra! He and the bumbling Mutants have made it their goal to stop the Thundercats by any means necessary, but of course the Thundercats have other plans!

title: Clementine's Beach Birthday
description: Caillou watches a ninja tv show and wants to learn Karate.

title: Una Extrana Conexion
description: Drago lidera a los Bakugan contra la amenaza de Tiko, para proteger una poderosa fuente de energía.

title: Caillou the Ninja
description: Caillou watches a ninja tv show and wants to learn Karate.

title: El Camino en el Calabozo
description: En su misión de derrotar al Rey Vangelis, Cole, Wu y Vania unen fuerzas con "Los de abajo" para encontrar una forma de salir del fondo de la montaña.

title: Caillou and the Protest
description: Caillou and Clementine encounter a march against racism while out selling cookies.

title: Caillou at the Fairground
description: Caillou wonders off accidentally at the fairgound.

title: Trailer Trashed
description: Muscle Man's trailer fails a health inspection and he wants to keep it at all costs.

title: Grief Bringer
description: Nya and Kai, who have become the respective leaders of the Munce and Geckles, attempt to unite the tribes in an effort to defeat their mutual enemy, the Skull Sorcerer, who schemes against them.

title: A Day at the Arcade
description: Caillou and Clementine visit the arcade and play different games!

title: Where's Pocoyo?
description: Pocoyo plays hide and seek with us. Can you find him?

title: Tiempo de Sonar
description: Después de una serie de pesadillas recurrentes que afectan su sueño, Ben se niega a contarles a Max y Gwen lo que le molesta. Pero una vez que se dan cuenta de que el propio Zombozo está detrás de las pesadillas, Ben debe aceptar la ayuda de Max y Gwen si quieren ponerle fin al terror.

title: Caillou's Snow Day
description: Caillou spends a day outside finding different ways to play in the snow.

title: Caillou's New Year
description: Caillou and his friends try to stay away until midnight on New Year's Eve.

title: Industrias Dusk Parte 2
description: Benton Dusk revela que Los Fantásticos son considerados personas de interés por poderosas corporaciones como AAAnimus.

title: Caillou at the Circus
description: Caillou goes to the circus and has so much fun that he brings the circus back home!

title: Butterman!
description: When Tez threatens to destroy the town's butterfly habitat to build a bowling alley, Victor, Valentino and Sal must find the Butterman in order to save the butterflies!

title: Caillou and the Bee
description: Caillou gets stung by a bee, but learns that bees are special creatures that don't want to hurt people!

title: Caillou Cheats
description: Caillou struggles in a test at school and gets caught cheating.

title: Caillou at the Botanical Garden
description: Caillou and his family visit the botanical gardens, and Caillou uses his listening skills to get through a maze!

title: Backyard Sports Day
description: Caillou and his friends organize their own sports day and even try the high jump!

title: #LaBuenaLaMalaYLaBizarra
description: Las cosas van bien en la vida de Kara Danvers, como adolescente y como superheroína, hasta que comienza a hacerse responsable de cosas que no hizo y la aparición de un nuevo supervillano amenaza con destruir la reputación que tanto le costó ganar a Supergirl.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Carter and Briggs
description: Mordecai and Rigby enter a donut contest to win a cameo on their favorite cop show.

title: Caillou at the Toy Store
description: Caillou gets to choose one toy from the store, but there are so many cool toys to pick from!

title: Caillou and the School Talent Show
description: Daddy helps Caillou prepare magic tricks for the school talent show!

title: Alienigenas del Pasado, Presente
description: Cuando Ben encuentra un video en Internet en el que Cannonbolt destruye un laboratorio informático, el equipo Tennyson debe correr a State U para encontrar al impostor. Pero una vez que Ben descubra que una versión a vapor de su alienígena es la que está aterrorizando al campus, deberá derribar al hombre que está detrás de la máquina: iVapor Smythe!

title: Simon por siempre
description: Duncan y Leshawna tratan de aprovecharse del amor de Izzy por el juego de Simón Dice.

title: Blenanas
description: Finn's latest literary work is met with only derision so he sets out to prove all the naysayers wrong.

title: Jelly Wrestle Rumble!
description: Huckleberry Hound hosts a wrestling tournament so that his childhood hero, the Funky Phantom, can relive his glory days.

title: That's the Stuff
description: While touring a space museum, Ben's excitement multiplies when he learns that recently discovered space stuff is being examined inside the museum's lab. Once the stuff comes to life and the shape-shifting goo replicates our hero, Ben must look within if he is to stop the case of mistaken identity.

title: Dawn of the Donut
description: Dr. Fox's plans to deliver donuts all over the Unikingdom are sidetracked by Unikitty's reluctance to follow instructions.

title: Relaxation Land
description: Uncle Grandpa's relaxing weekend getaway quickly becomes a spooky nightmare for Pizza Steve.

title: Things That Go Plunk
description: A shy, puny member of the Bad Crowd shows up at the Cloudseeker claiming he's been kicked out of Blusterland for being nice. The Bears, leery at first, take him in despite Grumpy's suspicions that he is in cahoots with Bluster. It appears Grumpy is right - but thanks to the Care Bears, the little guy turns into a good friend with the courage to thwart Bluster's latest scheme.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Eye Spy
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, are traveling on the back of a truck from Montana to Utah. Charlie wants to play a game of Eye Spy. He finds more and more obvious objects for Frank to spy but Frank isn't quite getting the hang of it. Yet!

title: Driving Miss Crazy
description: Duncan leads Beth to believe she's broken his battery-powered bike and makes her chauffeur him around in a wagon for the day as punishment.

title: The Treasure Chest/A Camping We Will Go/Chopsticks/A Special Dog
description: Caillou is helping Mom clean out the attic./The family goes away for a weekend of camping in the woods./Caillou has dinner at Sarah's house and discovers new foods and a new way to eat them./Caillou and Mom meet a fascinating woman in the park.

title: The Magical Box
description: Three baby bear brothers are granted a magical box that can transport them to any place in the universe.

title: Pequena graduacion
description: Steven y las Gemas celebran la primera clase de graduados de la Escuela Madre.

title: Freezer Burn
description: Batman and Firestorm team up to fight their respective cold villains, Mr. Freeze and Killer Frost. Complications arise when Firestorm's infatuation for the wily Ms. Frost gets the best of him.

title: Fiebre de la Baya de Azúcar
description: Mao Mao intenta ocultar su amor por el pastel de fruta.

title: Caillou's Halloween Party
description: Caillou's friends come to his house for a fun and spooky Halloween party.

title: Growing
description: Meet Bing and his friends… Join us and celebrate the noisy, joyful, messy reality of preschool life.

title: Not for the Paint of Heart
description: When Izzy believes that Chef wants her to "Rise to the Challenge" of destroying the daycare with art, she gets some magic paint to bring all her creations to life.

title: Caillou and the Real-Life Video Game
description: Caillou plays Dig-and-Build outside on a sunny day.

title: Caillou's Great Escape
description: Caillou is sent to his room as punishment, but tries to escape and to see his friends.

title: Luthor in Paradise
description: With the aid of Circe the Witch, Luthor travels to Paradise Island to steal an artifact that will give him god-like powers. When Superman and Batman arrive on the island to bring him back, they find that they're almost as popular with the Amazons as Luthor on this woman-only island.

title: Him Diddle Riddle
description: The Powerpuff Girls must solve a series of Him's riddles to keep the Professor from having to pay.

title: Strong Armed
description: When Bubbles breaks her arm and gets a powerful robotic cast, she must learn to stop being timid and embrace her smashy side to defeat the sleazy, sinister Pack Rat!

title: Caillou the Santa Helper
description: Caillou helps Santa deliver presents when Rudolph gets sick!

title: Caillou Bakes a Cake
description: Caillou helps Mommy bake a special cake for Leo's birthday party!

title: El dia del hamster
description: Owen toma el trabajo de cuidar al hamster de la clase y descubre que es malvado.

title: The Darkest Hour
description: Forced to flee by the arrival of Grief-Bringer, the ninja, the Munce and the Geckles take refuge in the Geckle Strong-Cave. But the bitter feud between Munce and Geckles threatens to tear them apart, just when unity is needed most…when they are about to confront the Skull Sorcerer and Grief-Bringer!

title: Stray Bullet
description: In order to save an innocent squirrel, Bubbles gives him a dash of Chemical X, giving him some super squirrel powers.

title: Caillou and the Easter Bunny
description: Caillou is excited the Easter Bunny is coming and cannot sleep!

title: Unikitty and the Ice Pop Factory
description: An eccentric figure announces a contest to tour her marvelous ice pop factory, sending the gang on a frantic quest to find the winning popsicle stick.

title: Rage of the Red Lanterns
description: Chased by the Red Lanterns, Lobo seeks sanctuary with the Justice League. As the League attempts to stave off the Red Lanterns, Lobo reveals the real reason he wants shelter in the Watchtower, he wants access to a powerful space weapon being held by our heroes.

title: Jefe de Cocina
description: Mao Mao se enfrenta a Colosal en una competencia para determinar si cocinar (y ser un héroe) es un arte o una ciencia.

title: El Ascenso
description: Cole, los de abajo, la princesa Vania y Wu salen de la montaña para enfrentarse al malvado Hechicero Calavera.

title: Meet Panthro
description: Panthro may be the strongest cat on Third Earth, but one of his biggest strengths is that he can fix anything!  And the rest of the Thundercats break enough stuff to really put his skills to the test, but it's nothing a pro like Panthro can't handle.

title: Simons Are Forever
description: Duncan and Leshawna try to take advantage of Izzy's love for the game of Simon Says.

title: Hit the Diamond
description: Steven and the Gems play an old fashioned game of baseball.

title: Sugar Berry Fever
description: Mao Mao tries to hide his love of cobbler.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: A Change of Face
description: In Salem Massachusetts, Ben, Gwen and Max once again go up against Charmcaster, whose goal is to switch souls with Ben and possess the Omnitrix. However, Charmcaster first accidentally switches identities with Gwen, and then as spells fly back and forth, Ben and Gwen even end up in one another's bodies before they team up to get rid of Charmcaster once and for all.

title: Dinosaur Museum
description: Caillou's class takes a field trip to the Museum!

title: Dreamtime
description: After a series of reoccurring nightmares affect his sleep, Ben refuses to open up to Max and Gwen about what's bothering him, but once they realize Zombozo himself is behind it, Ben must accept Max and Gwen's help if they are going to put a stop to the terror.

title: Poacher Patrol
description: When Don bestows Val the responsibility of patrolling the lake, Val takes it too far and stops who he believes to be a poacher -- with disastrous consequences.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Rivals
description: From Trigon to Terra to Darkseid, Robin counts down the worst of the worst: the greatest villains to ever challenge the Teen Titans!

title: T.G.I.S
description: The Secret Saturdays come to Bellwood to investigate a rash of chupacabra attacks.

title: The Feels
description: While Max and Gwen revel in the holiday spirit of Winter Wonderland, Ben couldn't be more unamused and focused on the toys, but once the Weatherheads set their sights on Winter Wonderland as their next target, our hero must become one with his emotion if he is to save the town.

title: Fuera de Mi Cabeza
description: iAxel debe ayudar a Sarge y Bobbie a aprender a caminar en los zapatos del otro, literalmente, después de que Luka involuntariamente cambia las cabezas de los juguetes!

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Intergalactic Games
description: Super Hero High is facing off against Korugar Academy in the Intergalactic Games, but Lena Luthor takes advantage of the gathering of supers to enact her villainous plan.

title: Pesadilla de Verano
description: Drago y los otros Bakugan de Los Fantásticos se enfrentan a una nueva y poderosa amenaza, solo para dejarlos preguntándose si todo habrá sido un sueño.

title: Caillou on the Fourth of July
description: Caillou goes to the lake to celebrate the Fourth of July.

title: Gotta Kiss Them All
description: Augie and Yakky play a VR game that has real-world consequences.

title: Caillou at the Parade
description: Caillou and his family go to see a parade!

title: Caillou the Skateboarder
description: Caillou tries skateboarding again after falling the first time!

title: Old Man Teo
description: When Vic and Val are tasked to volunteer at an Old Folks' Home, Val becomes buddies with the oldest, crankiest person in Monte Macabre and helps him reclaim his youthful power.

title: Rooms
description: The Bears switch bedrooms for the night and get a glimpse of the living space of one of their brothers. But the deeper they go, hidden secrets are revealed.

title: A Holiday Story
description: Santa Claus enlists Beast Boy's help in getting him back into the Holiday Mob, which is run by Baby New Year.

title: Countdown
description: Axel has to clean up the living room in time for his uncle's dinner party, but trying to do too much at once leaves him stuck as a toy with Orangutank on the loose and less than an hour until the guests arrive.

title: Caillou the Knight
description: Caillou faces a fierce dragon that tries to steal his spaghetti!

title: Caillou at the Science Fair
description: Caillou and Leo make an erupting volcano for the science fair!

title: Caillou on World Book Day
description: Caillou chooses a new adventure to read using his free book voucher!

title: Gem Drill
description: Steven takes a journey deep underground.

title: Viking Caillou
description: Caillou learns about Vikings at school.

title: Filthy Rich
description: What does it take to be truly content? Whatever it takes, Apple and Onion are going to achieve it.

title: Caillou the Soccer Player
description: Caillou learns how to work together to make soccer fun!

title: Losing Ice
description: Feeling unappreciated, Ice Bear leaves his brothers to be the chef of a restaurant. Desperate to fill the void, Grizz and Panda look for Ice Bear's replacement.

title: Prince Starling's Quest
description: Lion-O is happily playing with Snarf in their "Frolicking Field" and doesn't have a care in the world, unfortunately he's accidentally stomping all over the miniature village of the Micrits! The tiny people want to defeat the "giant orange monster" but such a quest would require a brave hero. Luckily, the Micrits have such a hero: Prince Starling! Now, let us the tell you the epic tale of Prince Starling as he journeys to find the fountain of growth and defeat the wicked Lion-O, who has no idea any of this is going on!

title: Cool Cubed
description: The guys need to unfreeze Thomas' brain after he chugs a slushy.

title: Apple & Onion's Booth
description: Apple and Onion must save their favorite booth at Pizza's Diner from a Texas oil tycoon.

title: Caillou the Prankster
description: When Caillou tries out some of Leo's prank toys, his family is in for a surprise!

title: Caillou at the Pool
description: Caillou has fun while staying safe at the pool, and tries out the big water slide!

title: Es la cosa
description: Mientras visita un museo espacial, la emoción de Ben se multiplica cuando se entera de que están examinando en el laboratorio unas "cosas espaciales" que acaban de descubrir. Pero cuando esa cosa viscosa cobra vida y comienza a replicar a nuestro héroe con su capacidad de cambiar de forma, Ben debe buscar en su interior si quiere detener el caso de identidad equivocada.

title: Stop! Hamster Time
description: Owen takes over the job of caring for the class hamster and learns that he's evil.

title: Parada de Descanso
description: Con el Rustbucket detenido en la carretera del Medio Oeste, Ben se encierra con su tablet mientras que Max y Gwen disfrutan del hermoso paisaje, hasta que el equipo Tennyson debe involucrarse en una persecución salvaje de un jackalope.

title: Caillou of the Future
description: Caillou and Daddy play a VR video game at the arcade and try to win a prize.

title: Deep Space Vacation
description: When Gar lets KO and Enid take a vacation to outer  space, they get more than they bargained for.

title: El Bigote
description: When Victor lands an internship with Lucha legend El Bigote, he picks up some bad habits that start to affect his life at home.

title: Ratar-O
description: The ThunderCats have gotten so good at defeating the Mutants of Plun-Darr that it's basically become routine. That all changes with the arrival of the Mutants' old leader: Ratar-O, wielder of the Sword of Plun-Darr! Uh-oh!

title: Ferekh
description: Apple and Onion are put in charge of Falafel's beloved rooster but it turns out that other parties have a vested interest in it too.

title: Plastic Man Saves the World
description: Plastic Man feels shuffled off to the side as the Justice League battles Brainiac so he takes it upon himself to infiltrate the alien's ship on his own and thwart the villain's plans.

title: Caillou's Explorer Adventure
description: Caillou and friends come up with an adventurous plan to save Teddy from Cavegirl Rosie!

title: Monster Weather
description: Max takes the kids to a drought stricken Chicago to see his favorite golden oldie band perform at a huge music festival. Once there, our heroes cross paths with a deranged weatherman.
